meanings: (알지 못하다) do not know, (이해하지 못하다) do not understand
(경험이 없다) have no experience, be ignorant of
감사 How can I ever thank you?
감사 I don't know how to thank you.
감사 I don't know how to express my gratitude.

phrases.phrase: 너무 오래 머무르는 건 아닌지 모르겠네요.
meanings: 초대와 방문 I don't want to wear out my welcome.
It would not matter if I didn't know, if my guess is right
